pack_runtime.py::test_dockerfile -v`\n272: \n273: - [ ] **T7.7**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py` with full workflow tests\n274:   - `test_pack_full_workflow_python`: end-to-end Python pack\n275:   - `test_pack_full_workflow_java`: end-to-end Java pack\n276:   - `test_pack_result_fields`: verify result dict has all fields\n277:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py`\n278:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_pack_full -v`\n279: \n280: - [ ] **T7.8**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py` with CLI command tests\n281:   - `test_pack_cli_help`: `--help` shows usage\n282:   - `test_pack_cli_valid_workspace`: valid pack execution\n283:   - `test_pack_cli_invalid_workspace`: error on invalid workspace\n284:   - `test_pack_cli_verbose_output`: verbose mode shows traceback\n285:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py`\n286:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py -v`\n287: \n288: - [ ] **T7.9**: Create `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py` with metadata model tests\n289:   - `test_agent_metadata_valid`: valid metadata creation\n290:   - `test_agent_metadata_invalid_language`: invalid language → ValidationError\n291:   - `test_agent_metadata_invalid_build_mode`: invalid build_mode → ValidationError\n292:   - `test_agent_metadata_invalid_port`: port out of range → ValidationError\n293:   - `test_metadata_service_load`: load from YAML file\n294:   - `test_metadata_service_save`: save to YAML file\n295:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py`\n296:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py -v`\n297: \n298: ### Phase 8: Integration & Validation (ST-8)\n299: \n300: - [ ] **T8.1**: Verify pyproject.toml installation\n301:   - `pip install -e cmd/cli` succeeds\n302:   - `kubectl-agentcube --version` prints `0.1.0`\n303:   - `kubectl-agentcube --help` shows pack command\n304:   - File: `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`\n305:   - Verification: `pip install -e cmd/cli && kubectl-agentcu