ame, workspace_path, metadata_path, dockerfile_path\n387: - [ ] Error output: colored error message, traceback if --verbose, exit code 1\n388: - [ ] Port validation: 1-65535 range\n389: - [ ] Language validation: 'python' or 'java' only\n390: - [ ] Build mode validation: 'local' or 'cloud' only\n391: - [ ] `pyproject.toml` defines console script entry point\n392: - [ ] Unit tests cover workspace validation, metadata loading, Dockerfile generation\n393: - [ ] Integration tests cover full pack workflow\n394: - [ ] `pytest cmd/cli/tests -v` passes all tests\n395: - [ ] Coverage > 80% for core modules\n396: \n397: ---\n398: \n399: ## File Changes Summary\n400: \n401: | File | Action | Lines Changed | Description |\n402: |------|--------|---------------|-------------|\n403: | `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml` | Create | ~40 | Project config, dependencies, console scripts |\n404: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/__init__.py` | Create | ~15 | Package exports, version |\n405: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | CLI subpackage marker |\n406: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` | Create | ~80 | Typer app, pack command, error handler |\n407: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | Models subpackage exports |\n408: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | Create | ~30 | MetadataOptions dataclass |\n409: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Create | ~10 | Runtime subpackage exports |\n410: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | Create | ~150 | PackRuntime class with pack workflow |\n411: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Create | ~10 | Services subpackage exports |\n412: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Create | ~100 | AgentMetadata model, MetadataService |\n413: | `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Create | ~40 | DockerService (placeholder) |\n414: | `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/main.py` | Create | ~10 | Example Python agent |\n415: | `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/requirements.txt` | Create | ~2 | Empty requirements |\n416: | `cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/main.py` | Create | ~20 | Example math agent |\n417: | `cmd/cli/examples/math-agent/requirements.txt` | Create | ~2 | Minimal requirements |\n418: | `cmd/cli/tests/__init__.py` | Create | ~5 | Test package marker |\n419: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py` | Create | ~200 | PackRuntime unit tests |\n420: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py` | Create | ~80 | CLI pack command tests |\n421: | `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py` | Create | ~100 | MetadataService tests |\n422: \n423: ---\n424: \n425: ## Implementation Notes\n426: \n427: - **Design completed at Stage ST-3**\n428: - **Metadata file resolution order**: `agent_metadata.yaml` → `agent.yaml` → `metadata.yaml`\n429: - **Entrypoint inference**: Python → `main.py` or first `.py` file; Java → `java -jar app.jar`\n430: - **Dockerfile generation**: Preserve existing Dockerfile, generate only if missing\n431: - **YAML dump settings**: `default_flow_style=False`, `indent=2`, `sort_keys=False`, `exclude_none=True`\n432: - **Language templates**: Python (`python:3.10-slim`), Java (multi-stage Maven build)\n433: - **Dependencies**: `typer[all]>=0.9.0`, `pydantic>=2.0.0`, `pyyaml>=6.0`, `rich>=13.0.0`\n434: - **Console script**: `kubectl-agentcube = agentcube.cli.main:app`\n435: - **Integration points**:\n436:   - `MetadataService` — metadata load/save operations\n437:   - `DockerService` — placeholder for AR-021 build integration\n438: - **Error handling**: `typer.Exit(1)` on exception, traceback with `--verbose`\n439: \n440: ---\n441: \n442: ## Implementation Timeline\n443: \n444: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n445: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n446: | Phase 1: Project Infrastructure | T1.1, T1.2, T1.3 | Pending | 0% |\n447: | Phase 2: Models Layer | T2.1, T2.2 | Pending | 0% |\n448: | Phase 3: Services Layer | T3.1, T3.2, T3.3, T3.4 | Pending | 0% |\n449: | Phase 4: PackRuntime Core Logic | T4.1-T4.12 | Pending | 0% |\n450: | Phase 5: CLI Command Layer | T5.1, T5.2, T5.3, T5.4, T5.5, T5.6 | Pending | 0% |\n451: | Phase 6: Example Workspaces | T6.1-T6.4 | Pending | 0% |\n452: | Phase 7: Unit Tests | T7.1-T7.9 | Pending | 0% |\n453: | Phase 8: Integration & Validation | T8.1-T8.5 | Pending | 0% |\n454: \n455: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/45 tasks)**\n\n(End of file - total 455 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Project Infrastructure (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml` with project configuration\n  - Project name: `kubectl-agentcube`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775869693480,"end":1775869693503}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775869693508,"sessionID":"ses_285ebad56ffeDbH0G4AG4R8HWw","part":{"id":"prt_d7a150a540014brgumNhnWF15J","messageID":"msg_d7a14c96600127jIFEojtmh0cZ","sessionID":"ses_285ebad56ffeDbH0G4AG4R8HWw","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-efef7bf5f2ab4e619b21f60da58a264b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-020/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-020/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-020 — CLI pack 命令\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 |\n8: | Module | `cmd/cli` |\n9: | Language | Python |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: Implement the `pack` command for the AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`). The pack command:\n16: \n17: 1. Validates workspace directory structure\n18: 2. Loads or creates `agent_metadata.yaml` (with fallback to `agent.yaml`, `metadata.yaml`)\n19: 3. Merges CLI option overrides into metadata\n20: 4. Validates language compatibility (Python requires `.py` files, Java requires `pom.xml`)\n21: 5. Processes dependencies (Python: requirements.txt; Java: pom.xml)\n22: 6. Generates Dockerfile if missing (language-specific templates)\n23: 7. Updates and saves metadata with pack results\n24: 8. Reports agent_name, workspace_path, metadata_path, dockerfile_path\n25: \n26: ## Out of Scope\n27: \n28: - Docker image building (handled by `build` command - AR-021)\n29: - Kubernetes deployment (handled by `publish` command - AR-022)\n30: - Agent invocation (handled by `invoke` command - AR-023)\n31: - Status checking (handled by `status` command - AR-024)\n32: - Container registry operations\n33: - Cloud build mode integration\n34: \n35: ## Dependencies\n36: \n37: | Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n38: |------------|---------|---------|\n39: | `typer[all]` | >=0.9.0 | CLI framework with Rich integration |\n40: | `pydantic` | >=2.0.0 | Metadata model validation |\n41: | `pyyaml` | >=6.0 | YAML metadata file handling |\n42: | `rich` | >=13.0.0 | Progress indicators and colored output |\n43: | `pytest` | >=7.4.0 | Unit/integration testing |\n44: | `pytest-mock` | >=3.11.0 | Mocking support for tests |\n45: \n46: ## Deliverables\n47: \n48: | File | Description |\n49: |------|-------------|\n50: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `pack` command implementation |\n51: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` class with pack workflow |\n52: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\n53: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata` model, `MetadataService` |\n54: | `tests/test_pack_runtime.py` | PackRuntime unit tests |\n55: | `tests/test_pack_cli.py` | CLI pack command tests |\n56: \n57: ## Acceptance Criteria\n58: \n59: - [ ] `kubectl-agentcube pack -f /path/to/workspace` validates workspace structure\n60: - [ ] Creates `agent_metadata.yaml` if missing, loads from fallback files if present\n61: - [ ] CLI options (`--agent-name`, `--language`, `--entrypoint`, `--port`, `--build-mode`, `--description`) override metadata values\n62: - [ ] Python workspace validation: requires at least one `.py` file\n63: - [ ] Java workspace validation: requires `pom.xml`\n64: - [ ] Generates Dockerfile if missing, preserves existing Dockerfile\n65: - [ ] Python Dockerfile template: `FROM python:3.10-slim`, pip install, expose port\n66: - [ ] Java Dockerfile template: Multi-stage Maven build → JRE runtime\n67: - [ ] Saves updated metadata to `{workspace}/agent_metadata.yaml`\n68: - [ ] Rich progress spinner during pack operation\n69: - [ ] Success output: agent_name, workspace_path, metadata_path, dockerfile_path\n70: - [ ] Error output: colored error message, traceback if --verbose, exit code 1\n71: - [ ] Port validation: 1-65535 range\n72: - [ ] Language validation: 'python' or 'java' only\n73: - [ ] Build mode validation: 'local' or 'cloud' only\n74: \n75: ## References\n76: \n77: - cli-toolkit/design.md — CLI toolkit architecture\n78: - cli-toolkit/spec.md — CLI specification\n79: - AR-021 — CLI build command\n80: - AR-022 — CLI publish command\n81: - AR-023 — CLI invoke command\n82: - AR-024 — CLI status command\n\n(End of file - total 82 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-020 — CLI pack 命令\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-020 — CLI pack 命令 |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\nImplement the `pack` command for the AgentCube CLI (`kubectl-agentcube`). The pack command:\n\n1. Validates workspace directory structure\n2. Loads or creates `agent_metadata.yaml` (with fallback to `agent.yaml`, `metadata.yaml`)\n3. Merges CLI option overrides into metadata\n4. Validates language compatibility (Python requires `.py` files, Java requires `pom.xml`)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-020/spec.md","time":{"start":1775869693483,"end":1775869693506}}}}
