{"type":"text","timestamp":1775869743227,"sessionID":"ses_285ebad56ffeDbH0G4AG4R8HWw","part":{"id":"prt_d7a15c1b1001Qnc78Xw6fK1Xab","messageID":"msg_d7a153f72001QSY7CQ4dRrymKu","sessionID":"ses_285ebad56ffeDbH0G4AG4R8HWw","type":"text","text":"## AR-020 Summary\n\n**Completed:**\n- Design stage (ST-3): `spec.md`, `design.md`, `tasks.md` — comprehensive architecture, data structures (`AgentMetadata`, `MetadataOptions`, `PackRuntime`), API contracts, testing strategy, 45 detailed tasks across 8 phases\n\n**Deferred:**\n- All implementation (Phases 1-8, 0/45 tasks):\n  - Project infrastructure (`pyproject.toml`, package init)\n  - Models/services/runtime layers\n  - CLI `pack` command (`kubectl-agentcube pack`)\n  - Example workspaces (`hello-agent`, `math-agent`)\n  - Unit & integration tests\n  - Validation/integration checks\n\n**Status:** Design complete, implementation pending (0% progress).","time":{"start":1775869743225,"end":1775869743225}}}
